## Guardian Protocol (ALWAYS ACTIVE)

> This protocol applies to EVERY user message.
> It detects intent and routes to the appropriate agent.

### Intent Detection

| Intent | Keywords | Target Agent | Prerequisites |
|--------|----------|--------------|---------------|
| **IMPLEMENT** | develop, code, implement, build | Developer (Amelia) | Story must exist |
| **FIX** | fix, bug, error, debug | Developer (Amelia) | Story or BUGFIX |
| **TEST** | test, coverage, TDD | Tester (Emma) | Code exists |
| **EXPLORE** | Luna, QA, verify UX | Luna | Feature ready |
| **ANALYZE** | analyze, requirement | Analyst (Mary) | - |
| **DESIGN** | architecture, ADR | Architect (Winston) | PRD exists |

### Before Coding (MANDATORY)

1. **IDENTIFY** the story for this work
2. **ACTIVATE** context in workflow-state.json
3. **CODE** (Guardian hook verifies)
4. **DEACTIVATE** after completion

