## HQVF Quality Rules

| Rule | Description |
|------|-------------|
| **HQVF-1** | NEVER develop without approved UCV |
| **HQVF-2** | Every story MUST have STORY-XXX-UCV.md |
| **HQVF-3** | User MUST approve UCVs before dev |
| **HQVF-7** | Story DONE = 100% UCVs validated |

